title: One Piece Film: Red - Ending Explained

media:group.media:title: One Piece Film: Red - Ending Explained
media:group.media:description: SPOILER ALERT! The One Piece Film: Red movie is out now in US theaters and other countries, which means we finally get to see more of the Red Hair Pirates in action and learn a little bit more about Shank’s past. Let’s break down the ending and how it fits in the long-running anime series.
